  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4387587/" class="title-link">认字不简单</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4387587"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/qinjian/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1000490-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qinjian/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">博容</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-05 20:33:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4387587_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看过了瑞典人林西莉的《汉字王国》和张大春的《认得几个字》后再看流沙河的《流沙河认字》觉得认字还真是不简单的事。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
